lead_paragraph: Former Olympic gymnastics all-around champion Nastia Liukin said on Wednesday that fellow American Simone Biles is the best gymnast she has seen and predicts the petite dynamo will be the darling of the Rio Games.

headline.print_headline: Former Champion Liukin Calls Biles 'the Best'
headline.main: Former Champion Liukin Calls Biles 'the Best'
